  "markup": "\u003Cp\u003EPhotobiomodulation is both an Art and a Science. Last month we dove into the Science. We covered clinical decision-making concerning targeting, dosing to achieve the desired tissue response and how PBM is able to achieve pain abatement and tissue repair. \u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003EIn this webinar we are going dive into the Art of applying PBM. Topics will include blending local and systemic applications of PBM; when to transition from one step of the Priority Principles to the next and when it is appropriate to even skip one or more of the Principles. \u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003EJoin Dr. Chris Carraway for the February webinar to help sharpen your skillset by building on what you\u0026rsquo;ve learned in January when we Incorporate the Flow of Priority Principle into practice\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cbr /\u003E"
}]]></Value>
